The E-Pharma market continues to witness significant growth globally, driven by the increasing adoption of digital platforms for medication purchasing. One key segment that is experiencing rapid expansion is the application segment, where E-Pharma services are being utilized not only by individual consumers but also by hospitals and for government research purposes. The convenience and accessibility offered by E-Pharma platforms have made them an essential component in these diverse applications, further fueling market growth.

